Diabetes Gradient Boosted Trees Model

# front-matter
rm(list = ls()) #clear the workspace

library(tidymodels)  # for the tune package, along with the rest of tidymodels

# Helper packages
library(rpart.plot)  # for visualizing a decision tree
library(vip)         # for variable importance plots
data(PimaIndiansDiabetes2, package = "mlbench")

diabetes <- na.omit(PimaIndiansDiabetes2)

diabetes <- as_tibble(diabetes)
class(diabetes)
[1] "tbl_df"     "tbl"        "data.frame"
diabetes
set.seed(123)
diabetes_split <- initial_split(diabetes, strata = diabetes)
diabetes_train <- training(diabetes_split)
diabetes_test <- testing(diabetes_split)
# training set proportions by children
diabetes_train %>% 
  count(diabetes) %>% 
  mutate(prop = n/sum(n))

# test set proportions by children
diabetes_test  %>% 
  count(diabetes) %>% 
  mutate(prop = n/sum(n))
tune_spec <- boost_tree(
                trees = tune(),
                tree_depth = tune(),
                min_n = tune(),
                learn_rate = tune(),
                loss_reduction = tune(),
              ) %>%
             set_engine("xgboost") %>%
             set_mode("classification")

tune_spec
Boosted Tree Model Specification (classification)

Main Arguments:
  trees = tune()
  min_n = tune()
  tree_depth = tune()
  learn_rate = tune()
  loss_reduction = tune()

Computational engine: xgboost 
boost_grid <- grid_regular(trees(),
                          tree_depth(),
                          min_n(),
                          learn_rate(),
                          loss_reduction(),
                          levels = 3)

boost_grid
boost_grid %>%
  count(tree_depth)
set.seed(234)
diabetes_folds <- vfold_cv(diabetes_train)
diabetes_folds
#  10-fold cross-validation 
set.seed(345)

boost_wf <- workflow() %>%
  add_model(tune_spec) %>%
  add_formula(diabetes ~ .)

boost_res <-
  boost_wf %>%
  tune_grid(
      resamples = diabetes_folds,
      grid = boost_grid,
      control = control_grid(save_pred = TRUE),
      metrics = metric_set(roc_auc)
      )

boost_res
# Tuning results
# 10-fold cross-validation 
boost_res %>%
  collect_metrics
boost_res %>%
  show_best("roc_auc")
best_boost <- boost_res %>%
  select_best("roc_auc")

best_boost
gbt_auc <-
  boost_res %>%
  collect_predictions(parameters = best_boost) %>%
  roc_curve(diabetes, .pred_neg) %>%
  mutate(model = "Gradient Boosted Trees")

autoplot(gbt_auc)


library(data.table)
fwrite(gbt_auc,'/Users/malcolmzerbe/practice_r/diabetes/project/volume/data/processed/gbt_auc.csv')
gbt_final_wf <-
  boost_wf %>%
  finalize_workflow(best_boost)

gbt_final_wf

gbt_final_fit <-
  gbt_final_wf %>%
  last_fit(diabetes_split)

gbt_final_fit %>%
  collect_metrics

gbt_final_fit %>% collect_predictions()
gbt_final_fit %>%
  collect_predictions() %>%
  roc_curve(diabetes, .pred_neg) %>%
  autoplot()

final_boost <- extract_workflow(gbt_final_fit)
final_boost
